/-- Transfer preservation of colimits along a natural isomorphism in the shape. -/
def preservesColimitOfIsoDiagram {K‚ÇÅ K‚ÇÇ : J ‚•§ C} (F : C ‚•§ D) (h : K‚ÇÅ ‚âÖ K‚ÇÇ) [PreservesColimit K‚ÇÅ F] :
